       pmt-ric-sel-100.
           add       1                    to   w-tbf-ctr-001          .
           if        w-tbf-ctr-001        >    w-tbf-num-ele
                     go to pmt-ric-sel-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione stringa in v-alf               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           string    w-tbf-pmt-fas
                    (w-tbf-ctr-001)
                                delimited by   size
                     "("        delimited by   size
                     w-tbf-nom-fas
                    (w-tbf-ctr-001)
                                delimited by   size
                     "): [ ]"   delimited by   size
                                          into v-alf                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Stampa stringa in v-alf                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      60                   to   v-car                  .
           add       04
                     w-tbf-ctr-001      giving v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
